he time we worked together confirmed the positive feelings I had since the beginning. Martina shows to be both very bright and motivated. I am confident that she will devote herself to any task assigned and commit to any challenge or opportunity on her work-path. Martina is very diligent, she is a quick learner and has shown the ability to digest large volumes of new information and major interest in sustainability. Thanks to her emphatic personality, it becomes easy to coordinate in team-work. I particularly appreciate her willingness to take initiative and I am sure she could develop soon also managerial skills.  I recommend Martina without reservations!", "recommendations/2/name": "Martina Chighine", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Certified Travel Designer | Sustainable and Responsible Tourism", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/martina-chighine/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB-tmh0BO8vOOBluFAOyCiTurNqxwiQUAJY", "recommendations/3/context": "Simon worked with Alvaro but they were at different companies", "recommendations/3/date": "July 28, 2021", "recommendations/3/description": "Alvaro is a brilliant and gifted Tourism-Business Professional who is seriously committed to any challenge he needs to face and assigned to. Alvaro is able to maintain a very positive attitude, even during very stressfull scenarios so to remain calm and focused on the goal throughout the most difficult situations. He has an extensive knowledge of Asia, MICE and luxury segments, FIT GIT quotation and operations. Alvaro speaks and write 5 languages. Our work-relationship as competitors of the same Industry has always been challenging but at the same time fair and respectful!", "recommendations/3/name": "Alvaro Garcia Gallego", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Inbound Manager", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alvaro-garcia-gallego-532b9396/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABR21DYBuxbO6ZuDVTt7als2GQ9CYBHZ2dM", "recommendations/4/context": "Simon managed IRENE directly", "recommendations/4/date": "May 7, 2021", "recommendations/4/description": "Irene is a talented, quick learner, young girl. It is not easy to come across a standout talent like her. She is fast and diligent in performing every task assigned. I coached Irene during her internship at Asian Trails and I can assure that she is definitely a great resource to have in the company. I am convinced that, thanks to her commitment, she will be very successful! ", "recommendations/4/name": "IRENE PERRONE", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Bookings and operations manager", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/irene-perrone-aba851189/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACxxEe4BlEPvLvOBBaURuako6zIzjfTKQ-A", "recommendations/5/context": "Simon worked with Michael on the same team", "recommendations/5/date": "April 28, 2021", "recommendations/5/description": "In the short period we collaborated on the same project I noticed that Michael is very good with people and has the ability to respond to their requests. He was very committed and focused on delivering the main objective on time. I was impressed by his knowledge transfer skill and his ability to simplify and explain a complex system.", "recommendations/5/name": "Michael Abate, PMP", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Project Manager", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michaelabate/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAApfCyYBtFU63DyBwrUHLi22IXBZnIVZBow", "recommendations/6/context": "Simon worked with Filippo on the same team", "recommendations/6/date": "February 3, 2021", "recommendations/6/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Filippo for over 1 year at Asian Trails, collaborating on several projects together. Filippo is a very motivated and determined person, he is a great team member and always ready to support his subordinates too. Filippo has a great attitude towards work, keeping a positive approach also during the most stressful situations. I can add that he has great analytical skills, good vision of the marketing and communication with\nboth b2b and b2c clients. Furthermore, thanks to his management skills, I am sure he can perfectly adapt and lead teams to achieve the most ambitious result or target.", "recommendations/6/name": "Filippo Sala", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Group Director of Customer Service at Lotus Asia Tours", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/filippo-sala-49355368/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA5Rp-8BhveV-ULyrhiFJMo2LzOeBLCEeUQ", "recommendations/7/context": "Simon worked with Domenico  but they were at different companies", "recommendations/7/date": "November 29, 2020", "recommendations/7/description": "I know Domenico since 2017 when we hosted together the first “Mega Fam-trip to the Land of Smile” sponsored by TAT. He is very good with both colleagues and clients, does whatever it takes to help partners and gets things done. \nHe is very knowledgeable about Airlines Industry. The collaboration has always been very smooth and his support definitely made a huge impact on our successes.\nDomenico is a great professional! ", "recommendations/7/name": "Domenico  Di Benedetto ", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Sales Manager & Aviation Travel Specialist | Technical Director-Travel Agency | Cultural Ambassador, Italia&friends | Attending Social Sciences for Global Challenges, University of Pavia", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/domenico-di-benedetto-010565dd/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABlgzF0BFx0sxnvtaq6DjGbJbAAQ2yZahsA", "recommendations/8/context": "Simon managed Angelo directly", "recommendations/8/date": "September 3, 2020", "recommendations/8/description": "Angelo is a real Talent. I recruited him and enjoyed working with him during his first year at Asian Trails. We have been collaborating and handling multiple projects. His commitment and dedication to his tasks will certainly allow him to professionally grow more and more. I was impressed by Angelo's ability to deal with even the toughest clients – effortlessly. As a team member Angelo earns my highest recommendation. ", "recommendations/8/name": "Angelo Macca", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Manager, Travel Distribution - Strategic Partnership | MBA Candidate", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mccngl911/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABMHErsBoydBQdarOvqJo_RaRuAPvEr2Y-s", "recommendations/9/context": "Simon managed Michael directly", "recommendations/9/date": "April 25, 2020", "recommendations/9/description": "Michael was part of the Asian Trails Italian Market Team for almost one year. It was certainly a pleasure to have him on board and I am happy he developed his skills and work-related abilities with us. He is a good team-player, always available when needed, he can adapt to new challenges and never step back when it comes to face difficult and stressful situations. I am sure he will make treasure of what he learnt with us and will improve his professionalism even further ", "recommendations/9/name": "Michael Paolucci", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "I’m passionate about travel and currently based in Bangkok, working in the tourism industry to create valuable experiences and insights in this dynamic field.", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-paolucci-a4b746145/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACMr1lsBgFmQsgalxw3_0O9-S_UrhIwyPBw", "recommendations/10/context": "Simon managed Emilia directly", "recommendations/10/date": "April 20, 2020", "recommendations/10/description": "Emilia joined Asian Trails Thailand LTD through and internship program we signed with IULM. Since the beginning she proved to be very interested in the job and tasks assigned. She is a fast learner. After 6 months with us we promoted her Key Account Supervisor and I am sure, she will soon achieve even better results! I wish Emilia all the best for her career and future in the Tourism Industry.", "recommendations/10/name": "Emilia Sacchi", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "Customer Success professional in hospitality SaaS, leading global hotel onboarding and trials to drive measurable commercial impact.", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/emilia-sacchi-a06440117/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB0TKaYB1mJ2PmTnB31q5QgSpUrY4dsqLfQ", "recommendations/11/context": "Simon worked with Thanyaprapa but they were at different companies", "recommendations/11/date": "April 20, 2020", "recommendations/11/description": "K. Beam is certainly one of most professional Director of Sales I have ever worked with. She is supportive and it is a pleasure to work on specific projects together. I can only have good comments about her performances and the way she always handled any critical situation. ", "recommendations/11/name": "Thanyaprapa Ponyeam", "recommendations/11/subtitle": "My New Chapter", "recommendations/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanyaprapa-ponyeam-38971892/", "recommendations/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABOu_RkBX8x1DJV4G1bGXJLyi31QVvlIG0I", "recommendations/12/context": "Simon managed Dario directly", "recommendations/12/date": "May 23, 2019", "recommendations/12/description": "Dario is a very diligent, service mind person. He is definitely a reliable expert with good knowledge of all the booking, planning and assistance processes. Calm, self controlled and very nice to work with! ", "recommendations/12/name": "Dario Cassano", "recommendations/12/subtitle": "Head of International Sales and Marketing. We produce high quality cashmere knitwear and accessories.", "recommendations/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dario-cassano-0589868a/", "recommendations/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABMCfMQBQfolEZ2BZwNj8tNXI6y0YiBkAjM", "recommendations/13/context": "Simon worked with Sasinun but they were at different companies", "recommendations/13/date": "April 4, 2019", "recommendations/13/description": "K Sine is the business counterpart everyone would like to have! Fair, gentle, helpful and a real support you can develop many projects with. Since we started to cooperate we constantly grow our numbers at the property she is working for. A real expert in Tourism Industry!", "recommendations/13/name": "Sasinun Wattanasarankul", "recommendations/13/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Sales at lebua Hotels and Resorts", "recommendations/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sasinun-wattanasarankul-26808915a/", "recommendations/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACYZJjABJmw8C2yQ_jY1dBlUzr2KtR14B8I", "recommendations/14/context": "Srivilux was Simon's client", "recommendations/14/date": "March 20, 2019", "recommendations/14/description": "Khun May is absolutely one of the most prepared business partner I have ever met in my Career! We have closed some very good deals and double our production at Anantara Sathorn when she was working there. Calm, prepared and cooperative business partner! Always available to support when needed! ", "recommendations/14/name": "Srivilux Sirinam", "recommendations/14/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Sales - Anantara Rasananda Koh Phangan Villas", "recommendations/14/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/srivilux-sirinam-046701182/", "recommendations/14/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACssuvYBUZYOe3mDFjaos_UDOXvk2sPHRUs", "recommendations/15/context": "Simon was Anshu's client", "recommendations/15/date": "March 18, 2019", "recommendations/15/description": "Anshu is one of the most proficient and supporting Business Partner I have met during my years in Bangkok! We have established a very strong cooperation. He is always present and proactive. Thanks to the strategy we have put in place together, Chanalais have passed from zero to be in the top 5 best seller properties in one season in the market. I am very convinced, it is difficult to find good business partners like Anshu! Very Professional!", "recommendations/15/name": "Anshu Bhatt", "recommendations/15/subtitle": "Accomplished professional with over 16 years of experience in the Hospitality Industry", "recommendations/15/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anshu-bhatt1/", "recommendations/15/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhmIrIB11uVFSP18fGRkP20LF6KebicB7s", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Mooktida (Tau) reported directly to Simon", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "July 11, 2023", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I had the opportunity to work with Simon, and let me tell you, he's not just your average professional.\n\nNot only can he land big clients, but he also manages big projects like a champ. I've noticed this ever since I first got to know him. When it comes to challenging and complex work, he nails it every time, as he demonstrated as the Group GM of Vega Hospitality.\n\nSimon is a fantastic boss - driven, detail-oriented, and deeply considerate towards his colleagues. He has a knack for giving great advice and filling in the gaps where his team might be lacking.\n\nWorking with him has been a real pleasure, and I'm certain that any organization that manages to snag him as a leader is in for some serious growth and success.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Mooktida (Tau) Saengaram", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "🔅 Marketing 🔅Performance Marketing 🔅E-commerce🔅", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/tausocial/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdRUIsBJHztnJqzJiYINw1fvsdzzpkB6HU", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "🌟 Stefan managed Simon directly", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "February 24, 2022", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I am thrilled to recommend Simon Ruggenini – we worked together for four years at Asian Trails. Simone started as Assistant Manager for the Italian Inbound team and received a promotion as Inbound Italian Market Manager in the Latin-Italian Department in May 2019. \n\nSimon is a responsible, trustworthy person and a hard-working individual. His ability to understand customers' requirements helped implement tailor-made products for tour operators in the Italian market. As a result, Simon and his team increased sales and profitability for the Italian Inbound Department. Simon has an analytic approach and combines it with remarkable and professional customer service orientation. He often took personal care to help clients, even during weekends. He proved strong negotiation skills and built valuable relationships with key suppliers. Significantly while implementing a new reservation software, his leadership skills helped overcome challenges, and Simon gave valuable feedback to improve processes. Simon is an asset to the company and has my highest recommendation.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "🌟 Stefan Bruns", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Working with leaders and professionals of companies in the tourism, MICE, Events, leisure and hospitality industries. \"Bringing West and East together\" MBA, Certified Professional Business Coach PBCA, NLP practitioner.", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/stefanbrunsbkk/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABKsuVcB5J_UNSjmoujmXIt5EO8uxb4I_oE", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Niels worked with Simon but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "August 12, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "During his tenure with Asian Trails, I have gotten to know Simon as a diligent, team-orientated and customer-focused travel professional. His energetic and positive attitude, even during more challenging times, was exemplary towards our Italian customers. Albeit working for different department, I found Simon's working ethics and creative approaches, and contributing to the overall success of Asian Trails, of very high standards.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Niels Steeman", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Helping individuals and teams achieve commercial and personal outcomes through healthy and sustainable people performance practices", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nielssteeman/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADfgk4BRmaVBPDIJLTbYCPuxU606d2-z4g", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Simon was senior to Martina but didn't manage Martina directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "July 28, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I met Simon during my internship at Asian Trails Thailand and I can certainly state that I have been really lucky to have him as my first boss. He immediately made me feel involved and part of the team, he has his own way of being very professional and at the same time easy-going: he can handle every issue in a quick, organized and efficient way. Simon constantly tries (and succeeds in) empowering all team members and motivating colleagues to perform at their best. It’s rare to find someone with such relational and executive skills. I’m sure he will be a valuable resource in any business context and especially senior-management position, where he can express his full potentials. ", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Martina Chighine", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Certified Travel Designer | Sustainable and Responsible Tourism", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/martina-chighine/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB-tmh0BO8vOOBluFAOyCiTurNqxwiQUAJY", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "Alvaro worked with Simon but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "July 28, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "Simon is certainly a professional person with an innate talent for organization. Simon is  always willing to learn and ready to take new challenges in his career.\nHe keeps a very positive attitude which helps during delicated and complicated situations. Thanks to his experience and commitment, he perfectly leads his team and offer growth opportunity in every situation. \nSimon speaks 5 languages and he has very good skills in Sales too. For Simon is very easy to adapt in different cultures and environments always thanks to his character.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "Alvaro Garcia Gallego", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Inbound Manager", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alvaro-garcia-gallego-532b9396/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABR21DYBuxbO6ZuDVTt7als2GQ9CYBHZ2dM", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Simon was senior to IRENE but didn't manage IRENE directly", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "May 7, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "I had the pleasure to meet Simon during my Internship experience at Asian Trails. Simon is a great expert in Tourism Industry. Thanks to his guidance, I could quickly become an active member of his dynamic team. Simon and the team warm- welcomed me since day zero! He is an excellent motivator with the ability to transmit the passion that he puts in his job, his positivity and energy to every colleague. It’s rare to find people like Simon, he always tries to exalt the talent of everyone and creates opportunities to develop everyone’s skills in many different areas.", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "IRENE PERRONE", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "Bookings and operations manager", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/irene-perrone-aba851189/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACxxEe4BlEPvLvOBBaURuako6zIzjfTKQ-A", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Michael worked with Simon but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "April 28, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "I had the pleasure to work closely with Simon during the implementation of the new online booking system at Asian Trails.  He actively contributed with very useful inputs thanks to his extensive knowledge of the Tourism Industry and all processes involved. Simon is definetely a great asset to any company and has my highest recommendation. ", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Michael Abate, PMP", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Project Manager", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michaelabate/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAApfCyYBtFU63DyBwrUHLi22IXBZnIVZBow", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Filippo worked with Simon on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "February 3, 2021", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "I would like to spend some words to witness the great job performed by Simon when I was his colleague for more than 1 year for Asian Trails. Simon had shown great command of his role and high confidence in managing and successfully guiding a team of over multinational members. He has the great merit to keep a positive and good problem-solving attitude at all times. He is able to stimulate motivation around him so as to lead the team to achieve the most ambitious targets. I am sure that thanks to his vision, Sales and Marketing skills, he is suitable to cover any Senior Management role.", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Filippo Sala", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "Group Director of Customer Service at Lotus Asia Tours", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/filippo-sala-49355368/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA5Rp-8BhveV-ULyrhiFJMo2LzOeBLCEeUQ", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Simon was Domenico 's client", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "November 29, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "Simone is a very efficient Professional in inbound Tourism. Equipped with eccellent management and organizational skills, providing full assistance to customers. Passion for his job is a very important plus point!", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Domenico  Di Benedetto ", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "Sales Manager & Aviation Travel Specialist | Technical Director-Travel Agency | Cultural Ambassador, Italia&friends | Attending Social Sciences for Global Challenges, University of Pavia", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/domenico-di-benedetto-010565dd/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABlgzF0BFx0sxnvtaq6DjGbJbAAQ2yZahsA", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Edégli Einard worked with Simon but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "September 21, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "I worked closely with Simon during his time in Milan, Italy while we used to handle together both Mice and Leisure Groups and FIT. He is a very good colleague and I am amazed by his ability to continuously professionally grow. Simon is a highly focused person as well as analytical, his energy to make things happen is  contagious. I am sure that he will do great in any top management position.", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Edégli Einard Bedendo", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Guida Turistica presso Libero Professionista", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/edégli-einard-bedendo-99a4571b7/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAADJvKcYBAaF-5cNZNi8qmIWCsCAuvEhEZ-M", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Angelo reported directly to Simon", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "September 3, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "Simone's commitment and dedication to his job, together with his ability to keep the team always motivated, are only a few of the qualities that make him a great manager. He is a very creative and inspiring person, highly skilled in dealing with issues and finding new ways to achieve outstanding results.\nIt has been a great pleasure working with Simone and, as a team player or a leader, he earns my highest recommendations.", "reco