 valuable experiences and insights in this dynamic field.", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michael-paolucci-a4b746145/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACMr1lsBgFmQsgalxw3_0O9-S_UrhIwyPBw", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Simon was senior to Emilia but didn't manage Emilia directly", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "April 20, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "I met Simone when he was recruiting trainees at my University (IULM Milan) for Asian Trails. I decided to apply for the internship, and I started my journey in Asian Trails in July 2019. Simone was, and currently is, my manager and I can clearly state that I could never find a better boss. He is very motivated and passionate about the job and for sure he is able to transmit these feelings to his colleagues and partners. He is very aware of the market and of the field he works for and he is always willing to share his knowledge with the colleagues. He is very good in training and managing the staff. He is ALWAYS available and willing to help and support. His empathy and passion are for sure contagious! ", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Emilia Sacchi", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "Customer Success professional in hospitality SaaS, leading global hotel onboarding and trials to drive measurable commercial impact.", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/emilia-sacchi-a06440117/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAB0TKaYB1mJ2PmTnB31q5QgSpUrY4dsqLfQ", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Thanyaprapa worked with Simon but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "April 20, 2020", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "I​ have​ been​ working​ with​ Khun​ Simon​ more​ than​ 4​ years, he​ is​ very​ profestional, good​ support​er​ and​ always​ helpful with​ all​ critical issue.​ ", "recommendationsReceived/13/name": "Thanyaprapa Ponyeam", "